          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X00-07E2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-07E2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-07E2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>Hree merry lads you own we are;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-2" n="2">'Tis very true, and free from care,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-3" n="3">But envious we cannot bear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-4" n="4">«LD»believe, Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-5" n="5">For were all forms of beauty thine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-6" n="6">Were you like Nereus, soft and fine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-7" n="7">We should not in the least repine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-8" n="8">«LD»or grieve, Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-9" n="9">Then know from us, most beauteous Dan,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-10" n="10">That roughness best becomes a man;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-11" n="11">'Tis women should be pale, and wan,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-12" n="12">«LD»and taper.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-13" n="13">And all your trifling beaux and fops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-14" n="14">Who comb their brows and sleek their chops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-15" n="15">Are but the offspring of toy-shops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-16" n="16">«LD»mere vapour.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-17" n="17">We know your morning-hours you pass</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-18" n="18">To cull and gather out a face;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-19" n="19">Is this the way you take your glass?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-20" n="20">«LD»Forbear it.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-21" n="21">Those loads of paint upon your toilet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-22" n="22">Will never mend your face, but spoil it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-23" n="23">It looks as if you did par-boil it.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-24" n="24">«LD»Drink claret.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-25" n="25">Your cheeks, by sleeking, are so lean,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-26" n="26">That they're like Cynthia in the wain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-27" n="27">Or breast of goose when 'tis pick'd clean,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-28" n="28">«LD»or pullet.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-29" n="29">See what by drinking you have done,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-30" n="30">You've made your phiz a skeleton,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-31" n="31">From the long distance of your crown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-07E2-line-32" n="32">«LD»t'your gullet!</l>
          </lg>
